Packages that use org.openstreetmap.osm.data.coordinates
org.openstreetmap.osm Provides basic interface to write programs that work with OpenStreetMap-data.

org.openstreetmap.osm.data.coordinates Provides basic classes for working with coordinates in OpenStreetMap-data

org.openstreetmap.osm.data.searching Provides basic classes for searching for names and addresses in OpenStreetMap-data 
org.openstreetmap.osm.data.searching.advancedAddressDB This is the implementation of an advanced version of the AddressDatabase.
org.openstreetmap.osm.data.visitors Provides some visors to work with OpenStreetMap-data 
org.openstreetmap.osm.io Provides basic classes for loading and saving OpenStreetMap-data from the OpenStreetMap-Server and files 
org.openstreetmap.travelingsalesman OSMNavigation provides the infrastructure required to build a navigator/route-planner on top of OpenStreetMap-data 
org.openstreetmap.travelingsalesman.actions Complex actions that can be done in the gui or Traveling Salesman 
org.openstreetmap.travelingsalesman.gps.data

org.openstreetmap.travelingsalesman.navigation Provides a high-level navigating-library 
org.openstreetmap.travelingsalesman.painting Provides a classes that can paint the map, route and marked points into a graphics-context
